THIS CODE IS BASED ON 'node js' SO YOU NEED TO INSTALL "node js"
DOWNLOAD ALL THE FILES PUT IT IN A SAME FOLDER
INSTALL "npm" and then install 'vite' using cmd "(npm install -g vite)" USING THIS COMMAND
THEN ONE YOU IDE AND CHANGE DIRECTORY TO CLIENT FROM THE IDE TERMINAL "( cd client)"
THEN USE COMMAND IN THE IDE TERMINAL "(npm run dev)"
AFTER IT RUNS THEN OPEN THE LINK IN YOUR BROWSER
THEN OPEN NEW TERMINAL IN YOUR IDE AND CHANGE YOU DIRECTORY TO SERVER "(cd server)"
THEN USE COMMAND IN THE IDE TERMINAL "(node server.js)"
AND NOW REFRESH THE BROWSER IN WHICH YOU HAVE OPENED IT 
AND START USING IT
